{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And money was of no value in particular, unless you were able to buy something or exchange it for-- say, some people bought you some apples.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some brought you some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some brought you some bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had an advantage, because we were local people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Knowing the local Christian population, it was a help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Of course, amongst the Jewish population in the camp, there were also people who were not native to our town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they didn't know any of the Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We also received occasionally-- not received, but they were given to my father through intermediaries in the camp-- sometimes a little parcel, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which helped out.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Maybe some potatoes, some rice, whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Whatever they could part with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this helped us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Of course, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] going back to the [INAUDIBLE] I mentioned that to you, when we were made to give up all our valuables.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After being a while in the camp, and we-- we acquired a top bunk, which was the best bunk because it was always warmer there and there was nobody above you, I had my jacket hanging from whatever space there was between the top bunk and the ceiling of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think my father even knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I-- I-- I-- I felt through my jacket, and I was suspicious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I opened it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I found 100 zloty note sewed in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "If this guy at the [INAUDIBLE] Altov, his name was, Altov-- would have found it, he would have shot me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I didn't know it was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And another-- on another occasion, they had brought in some clothes to the camp to be distributed to the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
